.footer
    #contactModal.modal.fade(tabindex='-1', role='dialog', aria-labelledby='myModalLabel')
        button.modal-close-btn(type='button', data-dismiss='modal')
        .modal-dialog(role='document')
            .modal-header.text-center
                h2.modal-header-title Subscribe to Mailing List
            .modal-body
                form(id='contactForm')
                    .form-group
                        input.form-control(type="text" placeholder="Name" id="contactName" required)
                    .form-group
                        input.form-control(type="email" placeholder="Email" id="contactEmail" required)
                    .form-group
                        input.form-control(type="text" placeholder="Company" id="contactCompany" required)
            .modal-footer
                button.btn.btn-main(type='button' id='contactButton') subscribe
    .container
        .row
            .col-md-6
                h5.footer-title.animated-down-0-7s About Flow Control Industries
                p.footer-text.animated-down-0-8s
                    | Flow Control Industries, Inc. (FCI) is a specialty manufacturer of high-performance pressure independent control valves, delivering energy efficient products and services through a consultative process to increase building value and lower total cost of ownership.

                p.footer-text.animated-down-0-9s
                    | The DeltaPValve®, FCI’s flagship product, was developed by Founder and Chairman Paul Skoglund, P.E. over 20 years ago when he realized that more effective valves could revolutionize mechanical system efficiency. As an industry pioneer, Paul was the first to create the patented design, development and application of pressure independent control valves.
                p.footer-text.animated-down-0-9s
                    a.footer-link(href="http://www.flowenergy.com" target="_blank") FlowEnergy
                    | , provides a holistic energy intelligence and optimization solution that combines FCI’s proven hardware, advanced software and expert guidance to deliver unprecedented control, in-depth insights, and sustainable savings.
                .copyright.hidden-xs.hidden-sm.animated-down-0-9s &copy; 2009 - 2016. Flow Control Industries, Inc. All Rights Reserved.
            .col-md-6
                h5.footer-title.animated-down-0-7s Interested in working with us?
                .wrap-btn
                    a.btn.btn-main.animated-down-0-9s(href="mailto:info@flowcontrol.com") Drop us a message
                br
                div
                    .footer-title-green.animated-down-0-8s Address:
                    p.footer-text-contact.animated-down-0-8s 18715 141st Ave NE Woodinville, WA 98072
                div
                    .footer-title-green.animated-down-0-8s Phone:
                    a.footer-text-contact.animated-down-0-8s(href="tel:425 483 1297") 425.483.1297
                div
                    .footer-title-green.animated-down-0-9s E-mail:
                    a.footer-text-contact.animated-down-0-9s(href="mailto:info@flowcontrol.com") info@flowcontrol.com
                .wrap-btn
                    button.btn.btn-main(type='button' data-toggle='modal' data-target='#contactModal') Subscribe to mailing list
                br
                div
                    a(href="https://www.facebook.com/DeltaPValve" target="_blank")
                        img.svg.social__icon(src="../img/icons/Facebook.svg")
                    a(href="https://twitter.com/FlowControl_Ind" target="_blank")
                        img.svg.social__icon(src="../img/icons/Twitter.svg")
                    a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/flow-control-industries-inc-?trk=company_logo" target="_blank")
                        img.svg.social__icon(src="../img/icons/Linkedin.svg") 
